---
import Button from "../Elements/Button.astro";
---

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="left">
      <h2 class="title title--large">
        <span class="kicker">The problem</span> A rising lifestyle cost
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="right">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <h3 class="title title--small">Ratification of fresh food</h3>
          <p class="regular-text">
            The cost of living has risen with inflation, with has made access to
            natural and fresh food difficult for more and more Canadians.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="title title--small">Home shortages</h3>
          <p class="regular-text">
            As the demand for homes outstrips the supply, home prices increase,
            making it difficult for people with lower incomes to afford a home.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <img src="images/TheProblem.png" alt="Woman looking worried" />
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="title title--small">Housing affordability</h3>
          <p class="regular-text">
            The average price of single family homes in 2022 has exceeded the
            million dollar mark, making impossible for the working class
            families to have home ownership.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <Button href="#" text="Our Philosophy" />
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    margin-top: 10rem;
    margin-bottom: 10rem;
  }

  .container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 5rem;
  }

  .left {
    width: 32%;
    padding-block: var(--fs-12);
  }

  .right {
    width: 55%;
  }

  .kicker {
    display: block;

    font-family: "EB Garamond", serif;
    font-size: var(--fs-3);
    color: var(--red-700);
  }

  ul {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--fs-12) var(--fs-11);
  }

  ul li:last-child {
    grid-column: span 2;

    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
